es, Caves, Mountains and Jungle. here are tons of cool cosmetics that you can buy in shop and wear anywhere! There is a myth in mines, that the miners that mine for coal say to Monkes who stumble into mines. They tell them that they have seen a disfigured Monke roaming around but that's just a myth. There are tons of cool cosmetics that you can buy in shop and wear anywhere!", "short_description": "Welcome to Monke Tag, a Gorilla Tag fan game with Tag! There are 3 Game modes, Infection, Casual and Minigames. There are many maps to play in and explore. This game uses the Gorilla Locomotion System."}]}, "developer_name": "Monke Laboratory Studios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://monkeylabstudios.wixsite.com/studio", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Monke Laboratory Studios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://monkeylabstudios.wixsite.com/studio", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "1023770785722696"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "233470082685263"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1008292560384301"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1008292560384301"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1698872400, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1008292560384301"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "27462953